## NEW finding workflow

Full step-by-step: skill **`promote-to-verification`**. Summary:

> **‚ö†Ô∏è ALWAYS SUMMARISE CONCRETE RESULTS FIRST ‚Äî THEN UPDATE.**

1. Explore ‚Üí write `verification/vN_<name>.py` (`tfpt_constants`, `check()/summary()/reset()`)
2. Register: `run_all.py`, `script_registry.csv`, run standalone + `run_all.py`
3. **`bash build.sh gen`** ‚Üí launch **`tfpt-deep-sync`** subagents ‚Üí merge checklist ‚Üí edit papers (`\veri{}` in **body**, not index alone)
4. Wolfram if exact (`tfpt_readouts.wl` + README count + `GATE.WOLFRAM.01`)
5. Ledger row + **`changelog.tex`** entry (mention vN id)
6. `bash build.sh release` ‚Üí **`AUDIT OK`**; browser-check website
7. `make_manifest.py` last

Deep-sync completeness (every surface agrees): skill **`tfpt-deep-sync`**.

## Zenodo

