- Commands: `bash build.sh zenodo` / `zenodo-publish`

## Maintenance

```bash
. experiments/tfpt-discovery/.venv/bin/activate
cd verification && python run_all.py                    # ALL CHECKS PASSED
wolframscript -file wolfram/tfpt_readouts.wl            # ALL WOLFRAM CHECKS PASSED
bash build.sh audit                                     # AUDIT OK
bash build.sh release                                   # full pre-commit
python make_manifest.py                                 # last
```

## Invariants (do not break)

- Suite stays green; add vN checks, never delete
- Every `run_all.py` script: `\veri{}` in paper body + registry row
- Generated files never hand-edited (see `tfpt-core`)
- Wolfram count = README count = ledger `GATE.WOLFRAM.01`
- `\phiz` ‚Üí write `(\phiz)^n`; Planck mass: `\Mbar` vs `\Mpl` in `tfpt_4_frontier`
- No old-version framing ("TFPT 4.5", "Paper 3 shows‚Ä¶")
- TeX visual sanity: no overfull `\vbox`; tables >~35 rows ‚Üí `xltabular`
- `papers.ts` mirrors section content, not just titles
